info.name: hands-on-DevOps
info.description: A hands-on DevOps course covering the culture, methods and repeated practices of modern software development involving Packer, Vagrant, VirtualBox, Ansible, Kubernetes, K3s, MetalLB, Traefik, Docker-Compose, Docker, Taiga, GitLab, Drone CI, SonarQube, Selenium, InSpec, Alpine 3.10, Ubuntu-bionic, CentOS 7...
